%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^RED%^War Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

A more varied domain than one might expect, the war domain grants the priest with a wide range of abilities all centered upon battle. Some are designed to aid his battle prowess while the third is meant to help him seek out a particular foe.

The war domain contains the following spells:

Magic Weapon, Spiritual Weapon, Magic Vestments, Divine Power*, Flame Strike, Transformation, Powerword Blind, Powerword Stun, Powerword Kill

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Nilith, Kreysneothosies

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
